                    <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-brand-text mb-3">Enterprise ERP Data Migration</h3>

                    <p class="text-brand-muted mb-6 leading-relaxed">
                        <strong>The Challenge:</strong> A key enterprise client struggled with fragmented customer data
                        across legacy ERP systems, preventing effective segmentation.
                        <br><br>
                        <strong>My Solution:</strong> Architected a custom SQL-based data mapping strategy and
                        configured robust API endpoints to synchronize over 1 million records.
                        <br><br>
                        <strong>The Outcome:</strong> Eliminated data silos, enabling the client to launch automated
                        campaigns 2 weeks ahead of schedule.
                    </p>

